    "special": "<p>Any attacks from a Dustard will trigger the worst hay fever you have ever experienced. The sudden sneezing fits and mucus flow causes a -1 penalty to Skill until the end of the round. Multiple attacks will stack this effect.</p>",
    "notes": "<p>In the unkempt cellars and dusty corners of Troika, you are likely to find dustards. These cat-sized crustaceous pests fester in smut in order to build up a coat of dust on their bodies which they utilize for triggering their prey’s sinuses into secreting mucus (their food source). On their own, they’re not a problem that a swift blow with a broom can’t fix. However, when they start nesting and begin to double their numbers day by day, that’s when you'll have to give up the house. It’s essentially theirs now. Their existence exudes dust and annoyance.</p>",
